   <h1>The Troll&#39;s Bane Chronicle</h1>

   <h2>The fifth year of the new era: August</h2>

<p> In the 5th year of the new age on August 1st, Town Guard Bailey Thunnigan announces the death of Maj Sowle. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on August 1st, members of 'The Knights of Kallahorn' battle against the pirate Gerard. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on August 2nd, Town Guard Callith warns people not to go into the southern forest. He warns that a large spider has been spotted lurking there. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on August 2nd, Markous Salkamaeria asks for a lizard to teach him the lizard tongue and the ways of Tanora. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on August 2nd, The Halfling Ian Ironkettle announces the reopening of 'The Fluffy Sheep Tavern & Kitchen'. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on August 4th, Marius Eisenhauer reminds citizens of Trollsbane that they are forbidden to plant any tree or shrub within the boundaries of Trollsbane. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on August 4th, Sima encourages citizens to post their poems onto the town wall. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on August 5th, Sceraphyna announces the death of her brother Garian. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on August 6th, Sylathen announces that an 8th victim of 'The Executioner' has been taken. He declares that the victim Elder Arcadulus is his friend and he swears vengeance. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 8th, the Dwarf Durin Silberbart declares himself as the new 'viceroy' of Silverbrand. As a result he is accused of High Treason. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 8th, Sceraphyna announces the murder of her husband, Garth Mandred. She swears revenge. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 9th, Tialdin announces that the dwarf Durin Silberbart is to be removed of all his duties and arrested immediately. He is later pardoned by the king. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 9th, Pendar announces that Wilfrid Ellis has disappeared. He is believed dead. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 10th, Pendar announces that he and Caitlin Fergus have adopted a child named 'Rhiannon'. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 12th, Devrah Lioness announces that the 8th victim of the executioner has risen again and warns of more attacks. Later that day, the Halfling 'Merrin Poppyseed' was found dead outside the library, the mark of the Executioner on his chest. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 12th, Durin Silberbart announces the 'official tax list' of Silverbrand. He announces that Tialdin and Fjalara have not paid and will be denied access to the town. Remarkable he also bans some well respected citizens. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 13th, Carpenters Faladron Furnir and Thalodos Artemetus found the Gobaith Carpenters Association, which aims to supply quality goods for fair prices. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 16th, a man named Thalgul announces that he has taken his daughter Rhiannon away with him. This is met with anger by citizens of Trollsbane. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 16th, The Synode is accused of murdering three children. It is soon rumoured that the leader is dead and that several members have left. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 17th, several citizens of Gobaith help build a ladder in order to infiltrate Drakhens tower. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 19th, The Executioner kills an 11th victim; Callith claims to have seen him. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 21st, Callith makes plans in order to fight Drakhen. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 21st, Arynne Halfmoon is killed by lover Dravish, whilst he is under the influence of Drakhen. The knight Stephen Rothman is also killed. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 22nd, Sylathen announces that he is to take over the Knights of Kallahorn. It is met with much controversy, which is dealt with at a meeting. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 23rd, Rumours spread of Thalodos Artemetus's death, it is then proved untrue. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 26th, Nymus Notenfid searches for three elves that allegedly killed his family. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 28th, several brave warriors attack a spider's nest; many are hurt. </p>
<p> In the 5th year of the new age on the August 28th, Markous forms the Order of the White Flame. One of there main tasks is to fight unnatural forces and guard the cemetery. They are given permission to reside at the Eldan Monastery. </p>


